The fact mages are so divided in their opinions and views will NEVER change, and to be honest that in itself has nothing to do with VI's seemingly being unattentive to the mage community.  You just can not expect thousands of people to all agree on multiple issues and solutions, period.. no matter what the issues.  You'd do good to find 10 people who all agree in one specific set of details, but the entire community of mages, never.  But as stated, that has nothing to do with VI's not seeming to want to talk.  What crawls under their skin is being bombarded by highly emotional letters with no solid content.  Therefore, don't blame those who disagree with eachother (or rather, you) for VI's lack of attention, and that is in essence the direction you're taking with your post.<br>
